    {
      "id": "Q1",
      "type": "single",
      "title": "**分析階段 (猜測 $\\delta$)：** 給定 $\\epsilon > 0$，我們需要找到 $\\delta > 0$ 使得當 $0 < |x - 3| < \\delta$ 時，$|(2x - 1) - 5| < \\epsilon$。\n   整理不等式：$|2x - 6| < \\epsilon \\Rightarrow 2|x - 3| < \\epsilon \\Rightarrow |x - 3| < \\frac{\\epsilon}{2}$。\n   因此，我們選擇 $\\delta = \\frac{\\epsilon}{2}$。",
      "options": null,
      "answer": "",
      "kp": "",
      "q_vector": [],
      "explanation": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "Q2",
      "type": "single",
      "title": "**證明階段：** 給定任意 $\\epsilon > 0$，取 $\\delta = \\frac{\\epsilon}{2}$。\n   若 $0 < |x - 3| < \\delta$，則：\n   $|(2x - 1) - 5| = |2x - 6| = 2|x - 3| < 2\\delta = 2(\\frac{\\epsilon}{2}) = \\epsilon$。",
      "options": null,
      "answer": "",
      "kp": "",
      "q_vector": [],
      "explanation": ""
    },
